## Coordinate system

RetinalSim uses a fovea-centered retinal coordinate system (right eye, fundus view):

- **x+** = nasal (toward optic disc)
- **xвҲ’** = temporal
- **y+** = superior
- **yвҲ’** = inferior
- **Origin** = fovea center
- **Units** = micrometers (Ојm)
- **Conversion** = 301.5 Ојm/deg (Drasdo & Fowler 1974)

